<table width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td class="content">
      <h3>Hello <%= name %>,</h3>
      <p>Congratulations on your new rental property at <%= propertyAddress %> As your landlord, I am excited to welcome you to our community.</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
  
  <tr>
    <td class="content cta">
      <p>In order to simplify the rent collection process, I am inviting you to set up an account on our property rental app, <%= appName %>. This platform will help you manage your rent payments, maintenance requests, and communicate with me directly.</p>
      <p>Please click the button below to set up your account:</p>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
          <a href="<%= inviteUrl %>" style="background-color: #3498db; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">Set up your account</a>
      </div>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to reach out to me directly.</p>
      <p>Thank you, and welcome to our community!</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>